<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-hero">
      <div>
        <img src="/assets/dr-bluestein-about-me.png" alt="Dr. Linda Bluestein, MD" class="about-photo">
      </div>
      <div class="about-bio">
        <h1>Linda Bluestein, M.D.</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Your Specialist for Hypermobility Disorders</p>
        <p>Dr. Linda Bluestein has been practicing medicine for over 20 years and is a fellowship-trained anesthesiologist and integrative pain medicine specialist. She has a unique grasp of the conditions common to those with symptomatic joint hypermobility.</p>
        <p>As a dancer, sufferer of hypermobile Ehlers-Danlos Syndrome (hEDS), and a medical doctor, Dr. Bluestein has a deep understanding of these conditions. She has treated patients for years, lectured internationally, and authored many papers on hypermobility disorders.</p>
        <p>Working with Dr. Bluestein enables you to learn from the past 16+ years of innovative research and clinical experience in hypermobility disorders, pain management, and injury prevention.</p>
        <p>Dr. Bluestein works as an integrative pain medicine consultant in conjunction with your current health care team, and is not a replacement for your primary care physician.</p>
        <a href="/services/" class="btn btn-primary mt-2">View Services</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

